### WELCOME

GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/welcome HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET USER BY ID

GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/users/me HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET TASTINGS

GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/tastings HTTP/1.1
Accept-Language: it
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET TASTING BY ID

GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/tastings/{{tid}} HTTP/1.1
Accept-Language: it
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

